{
  "stem": "11274.1",
  "chunk_idx": 9,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 4.1,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 29,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "So it ended up that we spoke pretty good Polish, and we did a lot of reading, which maybe other children didn't.",
      "word_count": 22
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 29,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "So the teacher decided that I was good enough in the Polish language and she said I was a pretty good talker, too.",
      "word_count": 23
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 30,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "I, I think that's why I got the-- I got a speech from the national holiday which was the President Marshall Pilsudski .",
      "word_count": 23
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 30,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "He was the liberator what fought for liberating Poland from, from the Russians, from Poland occupation, and a hero, a Polish hero.",
      "word_count": 22
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 30,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And on the-- because of the nation being 90% Catholic, they celebrated not his birthday when he was born, but his saint day.",
      "word_count": 23
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 30,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "His name was Jozef, Joseph, and on March 19, I think, is the St.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 30,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "Joseph Day.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 30,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "There was a big celebration at front of city hall, all the dignitaries sitting on two benches on a veranda, and then the ones who had speeches would come up and stand next to a table.",
      "word_count": 36
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 30,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "I was so short that they had to put me on a little stool to address the public.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 30,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "And then the public means everybody in town-- because everybody had children in school-- assembled outside, the Jewish families and other ones, listening to the speeches and to the songs.",
      "word_count": 30
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 30,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "That teacher that I said, the lay teacher, she played beautifully the violin.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 31,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "So the songs-- there was first speeches.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 31,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And I had the first, and I think the last Jewish girl that had a speech, and she-- I think it was because of the language, that I mastered the Polish language better than the other ones.",
      "word_count": 37
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 31,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "Or maybe she thought I was a good speaker.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 31,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "I don't know.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 32,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "But I got this speech and nobody after me after I finished grade school.",
      "word_count": 14
    }
  ],
